text="Relational extensionality">Relational extensionality</fr:title><fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> be two sets, and let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R,S\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex> be two <fr:link
href="jms-00I7.xml"
title="Relation"
addr="jms-00I7"
type="local">relations</fr:link> from <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>. Then we have <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R=S]]></fr:tex> if and only if <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\forall {a\in  A}\mathpunct {.} \forall {b\in  B}\mathpunct {.} a\mathrel {R}b\Longleftrightarrow  a\mathrel {S}b]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
